
Convert PDf to Word

1. Go to https://onedrive.live.com    sign in with whatever hotmail account you have. That opens microsoft cloud drive. Its just the storage place for word excel online files.   kinda like google drive but its googles version of software in the cloud.

2. Click on Upload (Right below the black bar.. front and center) Upload your pdf.

3. click on your pdf and open it up. 

4. On the top left where it says “Open” click the arrow and click on Open in Word Online.

5. Click on Edit in word (Blue button under black bar)….click “convert”…. then “Edit”   (If you hit view will you have to click edit on the next screen to enable editing)

6. Now make changes… file save etc. 
